<!channel> - i know there’s quite a bit going on in the write up. Megan is in there right now responding to comments/accepting changes/etc.

I’d like us to work to have a tidy-ish version of this by EOD. Let’s make some judgement calls vs. suggestions so we’re able to read it as a whole. 

Do you think there’s a way to have a pretty solid draft by EOD to ship over to google? I know we may wordsmith further, but also know we need to work to have a draft today. 

Let me know if that’s feasible <@U0260V4K1> <@U1HKQRLMR>
just talking with Megan - here’s my proposal - at 10, Megan is going to go through and resolve all of the obvious things, to make the doc a heckuva lot cleaner
afterwards - I would love <@U0260V4K1> to take a stroll through, and review more outstanding and substantive issues when it comes to content.
then we can see where we stand on unresolved bigger issues, and then we’ll be able to assess where we need to go from there
does that work for everyone?

works for me, though I wont be able to get to it until after P+P if that’s okay
